{"word":"G5219 - ὑπακούω - hypakoúō - hoop-ak-oo'-o - Hearken","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπακούω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypakoúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ak-oo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hearken</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கீழ்ப்படி, கேள்"},{"paragraph":"to listen, hearken"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G191 - ἀκούω - akoúō - ak-oo'-o/191\">G191</a>; to <i>hear under</i> (as a <i>subordinate</i>), that is, to <i>listen attentively</i>; by implication to <i>heed</i> or <i>conform</i> to a command or authority: - hearken, be obedient to, obey.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1522/1522\">G1522</a>, <a href=\"#/G1873/1873\">G1873</a>, <a href=\"#/G189/189\">G189</a>, <a href=\"#/G191/191\">G191</a>, <a href=\"#/G3876/3876\">G3876</a>, <a href=\"#/G3878/3878\">G3878</a>, <a href=\"#/G5218/5218\">G5218</a>, <a href=\"#/G5219/5219\">G5219</a>, <a href=\"#/G5255/5255\">G5255</a>"}]}